  "description": "B013 Blessed — the Chromatophore Modulator, performed. Aftertouch (channel pressure) boosts particle separation ×0.25 — pressing harder makes the school scatter, exactly as a cephalopod accelerates chromatophore cycles under stress. Mod wheel contracts the school (cohesion ×0.4). At rest: cohering. Aftertouch: scattering. Mod wheel: tightening. Three states of a single organism under different pressures.",
